<b>Yes.</b>

897
01:00:32,800 --> 01:00:34,225
<b>That's me.</b>

898
01:00:34,630 --> 01:00:35,795
<b>Yu-jin!</b>

899
01:00:36,900 --> 01:00:40,935
<b>What happened to you?
Do you know how worried I was?</b>

900
01:00:43,580 --> 01:00:46,205
<b>What do we do? Sun-young is here.</b>

901
01:00:46,750 --> 01:00:48,675
<b>[ Just run them over! ]</b>

902
01:00:49,942 --> 01:00:59,942
<b></b>

903
01:01:07,400 --> 01:01:11,295
<b>[ Eccentric! Chef Moon ]</b>

904
01:01:32,590 --> 01:01:34,655
<b>Why are they trying to kill Yu-jin?</b>

905
01:01:34,730 --> 01:01:35,855
<b>Lim Chul-yong.</b>

906
01:01:35,990 --> 01:01:38,329
<b>[ He has announced that all wealth
and authority will be ]</b>

907
01:01:38,330 --> 01:01:40,929
<b>[ handed over to Mr. Lim. ]</b>

908
01:01:40,930 --> 01:01:42,925
<b>[ Chef Moon, ]</b>

909
01:01:43,700 --> 01:01:47,605
<b>[ we'll meet again
after time passes, right? ]</b>

910
01:01:47,740 --> 01:01:49,835
<b>Tell them to get ready.</b>

911
01:01:49,870 --> 01:01:54,205
<b>[ I'm going to go meet them one by one. ]</b>

912
01:01:54,410 --> 01:01:58,075
<b>You've looked so hard for me,
but you don't seem too happy to see me.</b>

913
01:01:59,920 --> 01:02:01,119
<b>Smile.</b>

914
01:02:01,120 --> 01:02:04,415
<b>You look like you've just seen
a dead person come back alive.</b>

